rea": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/264522386"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8PvU66nV3N42EAMaCDIwMjM5OTA4IJL0+dEFMAA4kQJAGnIJMjY0NTIyMzg2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1777084213.864171", "card_id": "Q_2030701766480748673", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 254}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "家长索要电子版试卷，被指责派头大「把老师当服务人员」，下班了，老师到底该不该回家长消息？怎么沟通更好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，「家长向老师索要试卷双方激烈争执」的对话音频在网络发酵，引发热议。 家长因孩子未领到试卷，转达孩子请求，让老师发电子版，被老师指责「不客气」「没礼貌」，缺乏对教师的尊重。 老师强调自己已下班且无电子版，反感家长命令式的语气，认为老师不应被视为服务人员。家长则感到委屈，否认不客气，指老师将个人情绪强加于人。 4 月 23 日，天津市津南区教育局工作人员告诉记者，已收到此事的转办工单，正在调查。同时，该老师已不在课堂上，正在配合调查。 家长索要电子版试卷被老师指责派头大，「把老师当服务人员了」，双方微信起争执，当地教育局介入：当事人已不在课堂上，正配合调查"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-f618617bbb55ff1fb2a59464fa3a38f8.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2030701766480748673"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI8PvU66nV3N42EAMaCTExOTI1Mzg0OCDF0KfPBjAAOPkCQBtyEzIwMzA3MDE3NjY0ODA3NDg2NzN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1777084213.865044", "card_id": "Q_655532760", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 63}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么现在铺木地板的人越来越少？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-20d87fc94165e0b148ec6fbfb68241f5_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655532760"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI8PvU66nV3N42EAMaCTEwNzk1MTU5OCCct/WxBjAAOMI